Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've decided to head to Elbaf!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?! Please don't go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was just kidding. I know how you guys feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So you're coming back, Usopp?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course I am, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys must like me so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that idiot doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:03:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone Finally Has A Bounty!\NA Pirate Group Worth Over 600 Million!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna! I need lumber! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, those two are extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from Tom's Workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're barely keeping up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It boggles the mind that they\Ncould work at such a crazy pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there isn't even the\Nslightest fault in their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna get anywhere by\Njust sitting here and admiring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show them what us\NDock #1 workers are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna! Guys! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered you used to collect junk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and built a bunch of weird\Nbattleships on this scrap heap island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't like me building weapons, did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. On top of that, they were\Nused to frame Tom-san as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by looking at this, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that your experience building those\Nbattleships wasn't a waste at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show Tom-san that\Nthe Moron-ky from back then has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this ship, going to the New\NWorld is no longer a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even before Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can resolutely stand proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought those two would\Nwork together to build a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...! What the hell are you doing\Ninstead of helping me with work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you keep making\Nunstable stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's none of\Nyour business, Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's with him?!\NYou should just kick out an idiot like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't say that. He's a fellow ship builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His shipbuilding skills are already almost\Non par with the craftsmen on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though what he makes is shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just always honest, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two will definitely become\Nworld-class shipbuilding engineers someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things are going,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like we'll be able to\Nfinish it sooner than we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg, let me tell you one thing.\NThis isn't just another pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You've put your heart into--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats went head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against not only Navy Headquarters,\Nbut the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ship they'll be traveling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, the mayor of Water Seven,\Ntook part in building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that becomes known, you could be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, did you forget what Tom-san said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, there's no such thing\Nas blueprints for a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the sailors who board a ship put up\Na skull flag, then it's a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they put up a seagull flag,\Nthen it's a Navy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you wanna build,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a man should be resolutely\Nproud of the ship he built!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Galley-La has been building ships\Nbased on that creed all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm giving you a hand\Ntowards achieving your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I feel that... I'm not in my right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I asked you to\Ngive me a hand, Stupid-berg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned your real name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your body, too, is like that\Nof a completely different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed at all.\NYou're just the way you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream... Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Tom-san back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna build ships anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't love ships that hurt\Nthe people I really care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're my goal after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to come back\Nand teach me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...build a dream ship someday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship that resolutely and proudly traverses
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even uncharted waves at edges of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream ship like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bites... My body... is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if I'll die like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no one on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrap wood... Scrap iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place makes me... feel quite at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something\Nabout my disabled body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... anyway, what's up with\Nthat funny looking body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Since my whole\Nbody became of no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rebuilt my body using iron\Nscraps and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet face to face,\Nwe yell at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you... and you\Nmay feel the same about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...glad that... you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with "I'm glad that you're alive"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm alive, he ended up\Nhelping me achieve my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite an idiot, too, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whoa, Luffy! What a coincidence\Nto see you in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a stroll...\Nbut, well, this must just be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do? I'll come\Nback and rejoin the gang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is pattern 53.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not being able to use it\Nunless they find me is a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should take\Nsome initiative myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! That's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are they all looking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Straw Hats\Nreally have become edgy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lost their cohesiveness without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, for everyone's sake, I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pattern 34!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah-choo! Ah-choo!\NGeez, that night breeze is cold!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sneeze loudly so that they'd hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the crucial moment. I definitely\Nhave to act like this is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, is that you over there, Usopp?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, I just happened to be passing by."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You shouldn't stay outside, you'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come inside and have something warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, yeah? Well, I know\Nexactly how you guys feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you need me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let bygones be bygones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're going to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new ship is coming\Ntogether quickly, and I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to somehow rejoin the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:12:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now that it's come to this,\NI'll come up with more patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! I brought some food and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you Galley-La guys, too! Take a little break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought you cold cola, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We chilled them good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! I was pretty hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you brought some\Nof this stuff, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san! Franky!\NGo ahead and take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have been working\Nwithout eating or drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can keep on going like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we can take a break later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... then I'll take you up on that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not a bad idea for me\Nto replenish cola and power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Replenishment completed! Super... Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, he is!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, what're you going to do\Nonce the ship is completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you hand the ship over to the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you've achieved your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like those guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention whatsoever\Nof leaving this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm gonna go back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna, you sit back and relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie, it's you guys' turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're so exhausted that we\Ncan't even manage a late-night snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are the very\Ndefinition of inexhaustible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a party once the ship is completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a short time, but I had fun with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally met someone worthy\Nof entrusting with my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I promised, I'm gonna build an amazing ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg! Why don't you take it\Neasy and get some sleep, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm feeling super energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching this, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were called a legendary shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your skills and spirit were\Npassed down to your disciples splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A log has been stored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Log Pose is pointing to the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all we need now is the ship!\NI'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He told us not to come until it's\Ndone because he wants to surprise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys know where\Nfollowing that log will take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It somehow looks like it's\Npointing a little downwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is. The next island\Nis a paradise on the seabed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! F-F-Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's wrong, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island, huh?\NI have mixed feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it reminds us of what\Nhappened in your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though they were fishmen,\Nthey were pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly right, though you're stupid,\Nyou damn jerk! I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island is a famous\Nplace in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful mermaids draw arcs\Nover the water and play with fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I be allowed to dream?! I'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do have young ones there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not easy to get to this paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about it being on the seabed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll see once we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the front page.\NIt's a recent newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fourteen more ships have\Ndisappeared this month."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil's Triangle,\Nalso known as the Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach paradise without\Npassing through that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sea, more than 100\Nships go missing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after they go missing, sometimes\Nthe ships will show up with no crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increasingly, people are seeing\Nghost ships with a dead crew on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts?! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can meet skeletons that are alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of imagination do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I definitely don't wanna encounter them!\NI don't wanna even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such creepy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens in that sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who encounter trouble\Nnever come back, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dark sea with deep fog. So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's a dangerous sea\Nwhere lots of disasters happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you are well\Nprepared before you set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the stories about ghost ships--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, wrecked trading\Nships and pirate ships--there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...legends of treasure ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find ghost ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the worry's just about getting lost,\Ndon't worry, as we'll have plenty of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure ships, huh? I wonder\Nif they have swords, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky asked us to bring you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream ship has been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built an incredible ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's already done?!\NThat was really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five top-notch shipwrights\Nworked on it day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:20:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys running that\Nfrantically for? You're out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, we came\Nto ask you a huge favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the wanted posters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, the bounty on\Nyour head has gotten crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the others, too, are wanted in addition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of having me explain,\Njust take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All seven of you now have\Nbounties on your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy, 300-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It went up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro, 120-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat Burglar Nami, 16-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Candy Lover Chopper,\Nthe gang's pet, 50-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Child Nico Robin,\N80-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot Sanji, failed to obtain\Na picture, 77-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sogeking's got a bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we sympathize with you, or well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you wanna say all sorts\Nof things, but, well... please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The favor we're talking about\Nhas something to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborg Franky, 44-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Bro's got a bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We somehow\Nwere able to get off the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Bro had no such luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he stays in Water Seven,\Nhis life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets caught again, we're not\Nstrong enough to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he probably will try to stay on this\Nisland because he's worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we got together and discussed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, please! You can\Ndo it by force if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take Bro out to sea.\NHe's a pirate's son to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go get our new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! So is that it, Luffy?! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Where are you, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The King of Animals that Overlooks the Sea!\NThe Dream Ship Magnificently Completed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
